channel.title: Oh wow...!
channel.description:
Well i was looking around moparscape, then looked in the download section and decided to download and have a look at one of the current servers, so i downloaded it, saw the 1.1mb [b]"Client.java"[/b] had to look in it, first thing i found was this: [url=http://javacisnotrecognized.com/pastebin/index.php?pv=view&id=163]I can't even paste it into this post its that big takes a few seconds to load because its that big =\[/url] Basically this backs up the theory of "over crammed class's cause the server to lag", i posted this on this site because i knew you lot would get a good laugh out of this and would probably cause a good discussion, don't start posting all this 'keep it on moparscape' because there are two reasons i can't do that
[ul][li]Most of the people on there think its fine, and normal[/li] [li]There is no general section over there[/li][/ul]
Even still like i said i posted this over here because i knew you lot would get a good laugh out of this and could cause a good discussion on the state of runescape private servers at the moment.
The Un-named went all hilter and moved this to the java section *Angry face
